00:31:19.209 --> 00:31:24.249
important to them,
that's connected to the organization's work,

00:31:24.249 --> 00:31:28.849
they describe it as
feeling connected to the organization.

00:31:28.849 --> 00:31:33.879
So we kept hearing that name, connection.
I feel like I connect with my work on a day-to-day

00:31:33.879 --> 00:31:35.469
