Now the bottom line on the research is that

00:36:36.220 --> 00:36:41.269
connection makes us better
in our personal lives and in our lives at

00:36:41.269 --> 00:36:43.230
work.
And it affects us all of our lives.

00:36:43.230 --> 00:36:47.260
It's something we go into a little bit deeper
in the work.

