It's in our DNA.
Fist bumps, whether they're literal or figurative,

00:43:55.720 --> 00:43:59.140
metaphorical, we
need recognition.

00:43:59.140 --> 00:44:03.950
It's almost as if we have this recognition
battery that the plug in to

00:44:03.950 --> 00:44:07.819
the battery is in our back at the place where
