00:44:07.819 --> 00:44:11.920
So we have to rely on the people around us
to charge our recognition

00:44:11.920 --> 00:44:14.630
battery.
And we need that, if it's not charged, then

00:44:14.630 --> 00:44:18.180
we lose energy.
But if it is charged on a regular basis, it

00:44:18.180 --> 00:44:22.329
energizes us.
It helps perform better in life.

00:44:22.329 --> 00:44:25.660
And I would encourage you that -- take the
initiative to charge the

00:44:25.660 --> 00:44:28.690
batteries.
To be the, you know, seize those fist bumps

00:44:28.690 --> 00:44:31.230
moments with the people you
work with, to encourage them.

